 and allow to set."},{"content":"Serve or store in an airtight container for up to a week."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To clean mixing bowl in step 4, do a self clean <b>3 mins\/60°C\/speed 6<b>.","Add 2 Tbsp chopped nuts and\/or raisins at step 4.","Use both milk and white chocolate for the drizzle. Melt milk chocolate first and drizzle over biscuits then wash mixing bowl and repeat with white chocolate."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 5m","18 pieces"]}